Definition: A unique identifier for a unit within a catalog.
A text describing the name of the cataloger, in any chosen format.
A text describing the collector(s) in any chosen format.
Examples:
''Ex. 1.'' Peter Andersson
''Ex. 2.'' Peter Andersson, Anne Andersson
''Ex. 3.'' P. Andersson

Definition: A text describing the observation, in any chosen format.
The name of a defined FeatureObservationType.
A text describing a single Identification (including e.g. taxon name, identified by, and identification date), in any chosen format.
A text describing where the Occurrence took place, in any chosen format.
Examples:
''Ex. 1.'' Frescati
''Ex. 2.'' Frescati, Stockholm
''Ex. 3.'' Frescati, south of Stora Skuggan

Definition: A text describing the normal physical storage location, in any chosen format.
A text describing the date of the Occurrence, in any chosen format.
A text describing the PhysicalUnit, in any chosen format.
